{"tid":737910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寸大台出錯 遭袁花buddy報復狂質","createTime":"2018-07-11T06:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T13:06:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"01fe742285330dfa7b040ca43a7ea5546458eba6","tid":737910,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180711/20446250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F20446250&d=ePjZ8s8nzOd0IjjNpBSjjxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d809f461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F20446250&h=b6de9d26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180711/20446250</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月11日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n寸大台出錯<br />\n遭袁花buddy報復狂質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180711/large/a1602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180711%2Flarge%2Fa1602a.gif&h=bab8d44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n娥特早前喺7.1傳媒茶敍時點名TVB新聞部高層袁志偉，批評有報道出錯促修正，搞到袁志偉俾行家笑兼面燶燶後，大台早前因喺2017年特首選舉前嘅新聞報道中，兩次遺漏部份候選人名字，包括漏咗除林鄭、曾俊華、胡國興、以及入唔到閘嘅葉劉同梁國雄外嘅另外7名候選人，被通訊局裁定違反選舉公平原則，向大台發出勸喻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大內總管嚇到狂咳<br />\n<br />\n據聞大台對此相當不滿，除咗前日以「有議員指選管會指引對候選人定義欠清晰傳媒難執行」為題嘅報道反擊，噚日亦派記者到特首辦喺行會前質問娥特：「林太，你自己參選過特首啦，你可唔可以講得出你自己參選嘅時候，有幾多人同你一齊宣佈參選，同佢哋全名係乜嘢？你又覺得呢啲指引係咪切實可行？會唔會檢討吓？」聽到大台尖銳提問，企喺娥特身後嘅特首辦主任陳國基突然咳到彎晒腰&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n娥特回應質問時當然無講仲有乜對手，只係話選管會同通訊事務管理局都係相對獨立嘅機構，係按法例同指引就每個案得出睇法，但不忘指會重新檢視報道選舉嘅指引有冇修訂空間，唔知大台收唔收貨？  <br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 娥特忽然好雙語 Waste time做人肉多聲道 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n八方析時務： 深圳示範收高球場　為林鄭上彈 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八方析時務：深圳示範收高球場　為林鄭上彈<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：娥特忽然好雙語Waste time做人肉多聲道"},{"pid":"6fc89e6d58d7ab2d10a33de7e3565def1738ee5a","tid":737910,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"Mr Xu is charged with two counts of sexual intercourse without consen<br />\nThat's the point why i hate women so much"},{"pid":"8d39f3ae449c88f4877394613099e229912a9757","tid":737910,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"CCTVB或成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"2b8210a6dc337eea7d48ec4c410f3fa99f4ecad6","tid":737910,"uid":43173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"on9, 條例係被傳媒用防止只報1個候選人，參選人都唔受約束理你都ON9。"},{"pid":"f3ec8547009c1717e108b1aa23d7c4ddb88b4f96","tid":737910,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n唔想做就執柒咗佢啦"},{"pid":"c56e8b2bda617a3d5629a23c728fd8425c958152","tid":737910,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"ON9, 無報名果D都要報導埋, 咁茶餐廳話參選D 阿叔都有幾百個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8a7c079915571971a3ece1673e10490a29e7f4","tid":737910,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"個記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問得出口都勁<br />\n真係好聽話既狗"},{"pid":"76e0fdd05204bc24902cbede7c502245fcd0bdf7","tid":737910,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df8a7c079915571971a3ece1673e10490a29e7f4","tid":737910,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"個記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問得出口都勁<br />\n真係好聽話既狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"呢單野又真係強人所難D囉, 參選人都要報........"},{"pid":"6d128bca8e7c749a7885dea454ee7ea213096ade","tid":737910,"uid":153458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl